      • customiseUpdateForm

        public void customiseUpdateForm(Form f,
                                P o)
        Description copied from class: DataObjectUpdateFormFactory
        Perform target specific customisation of an update Form. For example we can replace Inputs with read-only fields keeping the field in the form for information but disabling input.Note that this is called in addition to the basic customiseForm call. Default behaviour is to lock fields based on the form.lock.table.field property. Editing can be permitted for certs roles of the form.edit_field_role.table.field property is set
